OL,3,CCoventry City announce victory parade
OL,4,Croute
OL,6,FCoventry City FC have announced the
OL,7,Froute of their victory parade after
OL,8,Fbeing promoted back to the Premier
OL,9,FLeague.
OL,11,FCelebrations will take place on the 4
OL,12,FMay bank holiday, and will conclude
OL,13,Fwith a music festival at the War
OL,14,FMemorial park between 1-7pm.
OL,16,FSome fans have expressed disappointed
OL,17,Fas the route is not passing through
OL,18,Fthe city centre. Instead it will:
OL,20,FPlayers and staff will then travel to
OL,21,Fthe War Memorial park at 4pm.
