OL,3,CCoventry City announce victory parade
OL,4,Croute
OL,6,FThe route will pass pubs, community
OL,7,Fhubs, and residential streets, which
OL,8,Fthe club says it hopes will create
OL,9,Fopportunities for fans to come
OL,10,Ftogether to celebrate.
OL,12,FCoventry City Owner and Executive
OL,13,FChairman, Doug King, said: "We are
OL,14,Fdelighted to announce the route for
OL,15,Fthe parade to celebrate our promotion
OL,16,Fto the Premier League as Champions.
