OL,3,CCoventry City announce victory parade
OL,4,Croute
OL,6,FCouncillor George Duggins, Leader of
OL,7,FCoventry City Council, said: "The
OL,8,Fwhole city is in celebration mode
OL,9,Fafter the club secured the
OL,10,FChampionship title. The club's parade
OL,11,Fwill provide the opportunity for
OL,12,Feveryone to come together and share
OL,13,Fthe joy.
OL,15,F"It is set to be an unforgettable day,
OL,16,Fcelebrating an amazing achievement and
OL,17,FI am sure it will be a day to
OL,18,Fremember, and a day that will go down
OL,19,Fin the club and city's history."
